        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter">
                    <ab><title>2 Chronicle 7</title>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                        <l n="1" xml:id="Chron2-007-001"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וככלות</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            Da tigetkecoq Šelomo tefile etme da ol ot endi ol keklerden da ertedi
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            ol ʿolany da ol debeḥalarny da šeḫinasy H-nyn toldu ol ivden.</l>
                        <l n="2" xml:id="Chron2-007-002"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ולא</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            da bolalmadylar ol kohenler kelme ivine H-nyn ki toldu šeḫinasy H-nyn osol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            ivinden H-nyn.</l>
                        <l n="3" xml:id="Chron2-007-003"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וכל </foreign>
                            Da bar uvullary Jisraʾelnin kererediler engende ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            ot da šeḫinasy H-nyn ol iv istine da cektiler izleri byla jerge ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            posacqa<ref n="1" target="#Chron2-007-fn1" type="noteAnchor" /> istine
                            da basurdular da sikir ettiler H-ɣa ki jaḥsydy ki dunja-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            ɣadejin savaɣaty anyn.</l>
                        <l n="4" xml:id="Chron2-007-004"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והמלך </foreign>
                            Da ol melek da bar ol ulus debeḥa ete-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            rediler debeḥa alnynda H-nyn.</l>
                        <l n="5" xml:id="Chron2-007-005"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויזבח </foreign>
                            Da debeḥa etti ol melek
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            Šelomo osol debeḥasyn ol syɣyrnyn egirmi eki min da qoj iz egirmi
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            min da qutladylar osol ivin ol Tenrinin ol melek da bar ulus.</l>
                        <l n="6" xml:id="Chron2-007-006"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והבהנים</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            Da ol kohenler saqlavlary istine turarediler da ol Levililer šira
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            savutlary byla H-nyn ki qyldy David ol meleksikir etme H-ɣa ki jaḥsydy
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            ki dunjaɣadejin savaɣaty anyn maḥtav bermegi byla Davidnin qollary byla da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                            ol kohenler tartarediler byrɣylarɣa qarsylaryna alarnyn da bar Jisraʾel
                            <milestone unit="line" n="25" />
                            turarediler.</l>
                        <l n="7" xml:id="Chron2-007-007"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויקדש </foreign>
                            Da aziz etti Šelomo osol ortasyn ol qaḥranyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="26" />
                            ki alnynda ivinin H-nyn ki qyldy anda ol ʿolany da osol javlaryn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="27" />
                            ol šelamimlernin ki ol tuclu mizbeaḥki qyldy Šelomo bolalmady syjyndyrma
                            <milestone unit="page" n="190r" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            osol ol ʿolany da osol ol tirkini da osol ol javlarny.</l>
                        <l n="8" xml:id="Chron2-007-008"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויעש </foreign>
                            Da qyldy
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            Šelomo osol ḥyʒyn suḫotnun ol vaḥtta ol jedi kinleri da bar Jisraʾel birge
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            sine anyn ullu qahal astry kelivinden Ḥamatnyn ezeninedejin
                            Micrinin.</l>
                        <l n="9" xml:id="Chron2-007-009"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויעשו </foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            Da qyldylar ol segizinci kinde ʿaceret ki qutlamaɣyn ol mizbeaḥnyn
                            qyldylar jedi
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            kinler jedi kinler da ol ḥyʒny jedi kinler.</l>
                        <l n="10" xml:id="Chron2-007-010"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וביום </foreign>
                            Da egirmi icinci kinde
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            ol jedinci ajnyn ijdirdi osol ol ulusnu catyrlaryna bijenedoɣanlarny
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            da satyr jireklilerni ol jaḥsy icin ki qyldy H Davidge da Šelomoɣa da Jisraʾelge
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            ulusuna.</l>
                        <l n="11" xml:id="Chron2-007-011"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויכל </foreign>
                            Da tigelledi Šelomo osol ivin H-nyn da osol ivin anyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            da osol bar ol kelgenni esine Šelomonun qylma ivinde H-nyn da ivinde ezinin
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            onardy qylmaɣynda.</l>
                        <l n="12" xml:id="Chron2-007-012"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וירא </foreign>
                            Da asqara bolundu šeḫinasy H-nyn Šelomoɣa
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            kece byla da ajtty anar esittim osol tefilenni senin da sajladym orunnu
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            ol uspu bolma mana debeḥa ivine.</l>
                        <l n="13" xml:id="Chron2-007-013"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">הן </foreign>
                            Muna beklesem ol keklerni da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            bolmasa jamɣur da muna bujursam ol cegirtkege asama bitisin ol jernin da eger
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            ijdirsem elet ulsuumda.</l>
                        <l n="14" xml:id="Chron2-007-014"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויכנעו </foreign>
                            Da synyqsalar ulusum ki ataledi šemim alar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            istine da tefile etseler da qolsalar qyblalarymny da qajtsalar jaman jollaryndan
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            da men esitimen ol keklerden da bosatymen jazyqlaryn alarnyn da
                            onɣaltymen qaranjasyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            jerlerinin.</l>
                        <l n="15" xml:id="Chron2-007-015"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">עתה </foreign>
                            Haligine ʿenajatlarym menim bolurlar acyqlar da esitivlerim
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            qajrylɣanlar tefilesine ol uspu orunnun.</l>
                        <l n="16" xml:id="Chron2-007-016"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ועתה </foreign>
                            Da haligine sajladym da aziz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            ettim ol uspu orunnu bolma šemim menim anda dunjaɣadejin da bolurlar ʿenaj-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            atlarym da fikirim menim anda bar ol kinlerni.</l>
                        <l n="17" xml:id="Chron2-007-017"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואתה </foreign>
                            Da sen eger jirisen alnymda
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            ki necik jiridi David atan senin da qylma barca necik ki bujurdum sana
                            da resimlerimni
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            da terelerimni saqlasan.</l>
                        <l n="18" xml:id="Chron2-007-018"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והקימותי </foreign>
                            Da qajjam etermen osol taḥtyn bijliginnin senin ki
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            necik kestim sert Davidge atana senin ajtadoɣac eksilmesti sana kisi erklenivci
                            <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                            Jisraʾelde.</l>
                        <l n="19" xml:id="Chron2-007-019"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואם </foreign>
                            Da eger qajtsanyz siz da kemisseniz resimlerimni da micvalarymny
                            <milestone unit="line" n="25" />
                            ki berdim alnynyzda siznin da barsanyz da qulluq etseniz ezge Tenrilerge
                            da basur-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="26" />
                            sanyz alarɣa.</l>
                        <l n="20" xml:id="Chron2-007-020"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ונתשתים </foreign>
                            Da taslarmen alarny jerim istinden ki berdim alarɣa da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="27" />
                            osol ol ivni ol uspu ki aziz ettim šemime taslarmen qyblalarym alnyndan da
                            <milestone unit="page" n="190v" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            berimen any masalɣa da cajnavɣa bar ol uluslarda.</l>
                        <l n="21" xml:id="Chron2-007-021"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והבית </foreign>
                            Da ol iv ol uspu
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            ki edi syjynda joɣarɣy bar asuvcuɣa anyn qatyna verenliginden sortun bolur
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            tamasa etmekke ki keredoɣac verenligin anyn tamasa eter da ajtyr ne icin
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            qyldy H bulaj jerge ol uspu da ivge ol uspu.</l>
                        <l n="22" xml:id="Chron2-007-022"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואמרו </foreign>
                            Da ajtyrlar anyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            icin ki kemistiler osol H-ny Tenrisin atalarynyn ki cyɣardy alarny
                            jerinden Micri-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            nin da tutundular ezge Tenrilerden da basurdular alarɣa da qulluq
                            ettiler alarɣa
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            anyn icin keltirdi H alar istine osol bar ol jamanny ol uspu.</l>
                    </ab>
